Story 

Once  upon a time in a forest, there lived a Monkey who recided on a jamun tree,
it was on the banks of a river in the same forest there also lived a Crocodile 
and his wife.One day the Crocodile came to the banks of the riveer and rested on the 
tree the kind hearted Monkey offered him some sweets the Crocodile came back 
the next day for more fruits and he loved them. As days passed by the Crocodile
and the Monkey became very good friends.    

One day the monkey sent some fruits for the Crocodile's Wife she ate the fruits 
and liked them but was jealous, as she didn't  like  her spending time with the Monkey.
she told her Husband , "If the fruits are so juicy, i wonder how sweet the heart of 
the monkey will be.Get me the heart of the monkey" the crocodile was not 
willing to kill his friend but had no choice.
